I dont think the real issue the monks have right now is being able to out tank a warrior.. The real issue is monks are Pull Bitches and where you as a warrior will tank 1 mob in most situations the monk that brings you that 1 mob just split it from 3 others.<br>
So when your tanking quads for 300 on 1 mob<br>
The monks that split that spawn will have the chance to get hit by 4 mobs that will now quad us for 500.<br>
The nerf dosent really affect me in a raid manner at all, as im good enough at aggro control i dont take much dmg.. But it affects my soloing ability and pulling ability greatly..<br>
There will be a lot more monk deaths while pulling if a FD fails.<br>
<br>
The cleric nerf is no biggie as there will be very few 10K Warriors.<br>
The Wizard Nerf is actually a good thing it dosent affect anyone but the manaburn teams at all.<br>
The Mage Nerf Sucks because They dont have the raw casting power of a wizard and alot of the time the pets get them in trouble.. CotH is all thats left..I really do hope mages dont get thrown to the wayside on raids. I like mages... =)<br>
Monk nerf.... may not beable to pull or solo anymore.<br>
